---

<BlogLayout
  title="Offensive vs Defensive Play in Scrabble — When to Open, When to Block"
  description="Master both offensive and defensive Scrabble strategies. Learn when to open the board, when to block, and how style matchups decide tournament games. Free strategy guide."
  keywords="offensive scrabble strategy, defensive scrabble play, blocking in scrabble, opening the board scrabble, scrabble style matchups, tournament scrabble strategy, hybrid scrabble play, scrabble board control"
>
